==English==
===Etymology===
Shortened '''[[no]] [[see]] [[them]]'''.

=== Pronunciation ===
nō'sē'ŭm

=== Noun ===
{{en-noun}}
#{{colloquial}} a [[biting]] [[midge]], a very small, annoying, flying insect that [[harass]] people out of doors, particularly in warm weather after sunset.
#: Suddenly a '''noseeum''' was in my eye!
#: Bill complained that the '''noseeums''' were making his life miserable.

